Wilbur Wants to Kill Himself;;72;;84;;R;;When their mother dies, Harbour (Adrian Rawlins) takes it upon himself to look after his suicidal brother, Wilbur (Jamie Sives). Years later, the brothers find themselves dealing with the sudden death of their father, from whom they inherit a bookstore. While working in the shop, they meet a hospital cleaning lady named Alice (Shirley Henderson) and her daughter, Mary (Lisa McKinlay). Harbour falls in love with Alice, and Wilbur's friendship with Mary gives him something to live for.;;Comedy,Drama;;Lone Scherfig;;2002;;Jamie Sives,Adrian Rawlins,Shirley Henderson,Lisa McKinlay,Mads Mikkelsen,Julia Davis,Susan Vidler,Robert McIntosh,Lorraine McIntosh,Gordon Broem;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wilbur_wants_to_kill_himself